wikipedia_page.main: Jennifer Jane Forwood, 11th Baroness Arlington (born 7 May 1939 in London, née Nelson) is the daughter of General Sir John Nelson (died 1993) and Lady Margaret Jane Fitzroy (died 1995), sister of the 9th Duke of Grafton.

response: Nelson married Hylda Letitia Grace Blois, daughter of Sir John Ralph Blois, 8th Baronet and Eliza Ellen Chapman, on 11 June 1908. He was the father of Major General Sir Eustace John Blois Nelson and grandfather of  Jennifer Forwood, 11th Baroness Arlingtonthe Peerage.com
